<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>qí miào zhī shén 迦南131</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 shén yòng qiān wàn gè bù tóng de bàn fǎ lái bāng zhù wǒ men,
 shén yòng qiān wàn gè bù tóng de huán jìng lái gǎi biàn wǒ men,
 shén yòng qiān wàn gè bù tóng de zhù fú lái ēn dài wǒ men,
 shén yòng qiān wàn gè bù tóng de huàn nán lái shì liàn wǒ men,
 wǒ yào zàn měi zàn měi tā de zhì huì,
 wǒ yào gē chàng gē chàng tā de jiù ēn,
 tā yǒng yuǎn shì zhǔ, tā yǒng yuǎn shì ài,
 tā de míng zì shì qí miào yě shì quán néng shén.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>131</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>